      <description>&lt;h1 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Privacy-First Design Principles 
    &lt;div id=&#34;privacy-first-design-principles&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    
    &lt;span
        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;
        &lt;a class=&#34;group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#privacy-first-design-principles&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/span&gt;        
    
&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Privacy isn&amp;rsquo;t just a feature—it&amp;rsquo;s a fundamental design principle that should be built into every application from the ground up.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Our Privacy Philosophy 
    &lt;div id=&#34;our-privacy-philosophy&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    
    &lt;span
        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;
        &lt;a class=&#34;group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#our-privacy-philosophy&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/span&gt;        
    
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Data Minimization&lt;/strong&gt; - Only collect what you absolutely need.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Local Processing&lt;/strong&gt; - Keep sensitive data on the user&amp;rsquo;s device.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
